    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>I see. It's just... even if I did reach out, it feels so performative. Like I'm just adding more noise to a world that doesn't really need it. Everything feels so heavy and pointless lately. It's like I'm just a burden on the space I occupy, you know? Like, the world would honestly just be a little bit quieter and easier if I wasn't part of the equation.",
