      "content": "i don't know... it just doesn't feel that way. it feels more like a math problem. like, i take up resources, i use up space and energy, and for what? to just be a cycle of breathing and working and being alone? it feels more like a net loss than a gain. like, wouldn't a little bit of silence be better than all this dragging around?",
